attribute-definition.description:
JSON object based on OrderAddressMap Variable, specific values will vary by return service. EX: {
            "name" : '', 
            "city" : '',
            "stateCode" : '',
            "postalCode" : '',
            "countryCode" : '',
            "address1" : '',
            "address2" : '',
            "phone" : ''
        };

JWT signing key ID. It is required for the JWT header. 
Example - jwtHeader: {
                    alg: 'HS512',
                    kid: '32b681ab-96e3-4181-90b6-54f0908c0a2b' // JWT Signing Key ID
                }

Optional JSON formatted object to override default standard feed mapping. The keys are Borderfree field names, and the type and source correspond to SFCC product attribute types and attribute ids.
{
    "id": {
        "type": "String",
        "source": "ID"
    },
    "last_updated": {
        "type": "DateTime",
        "source": "lastModified"
    }
}
See https://docs.borderfree.com/display/PSMD/Product+feed for Borderfree available attributes.
See https://documentation.demandware.com/DOC1/topic/com.demandware.dochelp/DWAPI/scriptapi/html/api/class_dw_catalog_Product.html?cp=0_15_2_3_7 for all available SFCC attributes

The Klarna Payments not available message on billing page. JSON string holding country code and corresponding message string. For example:
{  
   "GB":"Klarna Payment not available",
   "default":"Klarna Payment not available"
}
